flowchart TD
    A[Admin opens certificate detail page] --> B{Choose action}
    B -->|Generate| C[Create certificate]
    B -->|Send Graduation Email| D[Send graduation email]
    B -->|Recreate| E[Create new version]
    B -->|Download| F[Download certificate file]
    B -->|Delete| G[Confirm delete]
    G --> H{Confirmed?}
    H -->|No| I[Cancel]
    H -->|Yes| J[Delete file if exists and soft delete record]
